summary: Day 19: Nice system here. Each individual figure is intended to be looped over one another. Kind of creating a polyrhythmic...
caption: Day 19: Nice system here. Each individual figure is intended to be looped over one another. Kind of creating a polyrhythmic cycle. Interesting notion with the writing today as well. Left page is more abstract and right page is slightly more interpretive and concrete. An interesting idea to create a poetic work that translates itself.

reblog.comment: Day 19: Nice system here. Each individual figure is intended to be looped over one another. Kind of creating a polyrhythmic cycle. Interesting notion with the writing today as well. summary: Day 17: Above(Left): It’s a screenshot from google map of the area of Northern Mariana Islands(Guam). Above(Right): The shape...
caption:
Day 17:

Above(Left):

It’s a screenshot from google map of the area of Northern Mariana Islands(Guam).

Above(Right):

The shape reminds me of Matisse’s cut off piece, “dance”.

Below:

I made a drawing sketch in Processing to recreate the shape of the landscape.

summary: Day 18: Exploded chords. Gonna iterate on this for a moment. Excited to see what happens. Basically, just taking the individual...
caption: Day 18: Exploded chords. Gonna iterate on this for a moment. Excited to see what happens. Basically, just taking the individual notes from a chord and using them as the starting point for short musical phrases. Triggered by the “building blocks” line in the writing, by the way.
